{"tid":378401,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"話說尋晚係新浪潭好似被的士狗拒載","createTime":"2017-08-28T12:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T09:56:47.000Z","uid":42752,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02ba8df7b02b18e7e7f0ca712168580952b1c2a8","tid":378401,"uid":42752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:51:14.000Z","msg":"早兩日小妹係新娘潭撞車瓜左，咁我都要翻屋企啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朝早天熱又走唔到，夜晚call的人之常情啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次我見到的士想截啦，啲仆街竟然扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁上黎問下我可唔可以告拒載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：已經抹乾淨身體，眼球搵翻一個，手都有齊，但腳斷左<br />\n唔代表可以拒載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f5d06ef9b4a109c57fcf778b2a94b669a49abd","tid":378401,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哦</span></span>"},{"pid":"cd0f8657fcee5e69bfad8914d6178fc95222bbed","tid":378401,"uid":58209,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"落地獄啦仆街"},{"pid":"d2acca91ecc7c5c3720aa574217424370581aba9","tid":378401,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>落地獄啦仆街</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8087708a223ac9cfc8